snippet: Chanette Hicks scored nine points and made two steals in overtime as No. 24 Virginia Tech battled past upset-minded Auburn 92-87 on Sunday night....
lead_paragraph: Chanette Hicks scored nine points and made two steals in overtime as No. 24 Virginia Tech battled past upset-minded Auburn 92-87 on Sunday night.

headline.main: Hicks Comes on Late, No. 24 Virginia Tech Women Beat Auburn
